metadata.name: Dark Naughty Elfs #9191
metadata.description: The naughty elfs have just sprung out of nowhere and are now flooding everything in there paths. The Naughty Elfs Club will be a collection of 10,000 unique Elf NFTsâ€” unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. Your Naughty Elf doubles as your Dark Club membership card, and grants access to members-only benefits, the first of which is access to the dark lobby, a collaborative lounge for all. Future areas and perks can be unlocked by the community through roadmap activation.
